title: Ep9 Gossip at the Corpse Cart
description: This month, the gals share some "cheesy" headlines, a whole new crop of Coven Confessions, and a robust obit, plus they take a look at a haunted bootcamp experience and wonder why anyone in their right mind would want to participate. Tune in for September's edition of Gossip at the Corpse Cart!
